Summary: Colour Management System
Name: oyranos
License: BSD
Group: Development/Libraries
URL: http://www.oyranos.org
Vendor: Kai-Uwe Behrmann http://www.behrmann.name
Packager: Kai-Uwe Behrmann <ku.b@gmx.de>
BuildArch: noarch
BuildRoot: %{_tmppath}/%{name}-root
Prefix:    %{_prefix}

%description
Oyranos is a colour management system.
It is primarily developed on free operating systems.

Authors:
--------
    Oyranos     Kai-Uwe Behrmann <www.behrmann.name>



%prep
%setup -n %{name}-%{version}

%build
%configure --quick --enable-verbose

%install
rm -rf %{buildroot}
make DESTDIR=%{buildroot} install-icc
rm -fr %{buildroot}/%{_datadir}/doc/%{name}

%clean
rm -rf %{buildroot}

%post
%postun


%package      RGB
Summary:    Oyranos default sRGB ICC profile +
Group:      Applications/Graphics
Vendor:     http://www.littlecms.com
URL:        http://www.littlecms.com
License:    public domain
Version:    0.5
%description  RGB
The "WWW standard" sRGB profile and others

%package      lcmsLAB
Summary:    Oyranos default PCS profiles
Group:      Applications/Graphics
Vendor:     http://www.littlecms.com
URL:        http://www.littlecms.com
License:    public domain
Version:    0.5
%description  lcmsLAB
Special LCMS profiles.

%package      ECI-RGB
Summary:    Oyranos default Editing RGB profile
Group:      Applications/Graphics
Vendor:     http://www.eci.org
URL:        http://www.eci.org
License:    ECI-RGB
Version:    0.5
%description  ECI-RGB
The RGB profile maintaining perceptual equal lightness.

%package      Cineon
Summary:    Oyranos additional Cineon ICC Profiles
Group:      Applications/Graphics
URL:        http://www.behrmann.name
License:    zlib
Version:    0.5
%description  Cineon
Cineon ICC Profiles

%package      PhotoGamutRGB
Summary:    Oyranos additional ICC Profile for Photoediting
Group:      Applications/Graphics
Vendor:     http://www.photogamut.org
URL:        http://www.photogamut.org
License:    PhotoGamut
Version:    0.5
%description  PhotoGamutRGB
A ICC Profile optimized for digital photos.

%package      Printing
Summary:    Printing Profiles
Group:      Applications/Graphics
URL:        http://www.behrmann.name
Vendor:     http://www.behrmann.name
License:    zlib
Version:    0.5
%description  Printing
Printing profiles according to ISO 12647-2. These are CMYK
ICC profiles for ISO Printing conditions.

%package      target-fogra
Summary:    FOGRA Printing Characterisation Data
Group:      Applications/Graphics
URL:        http://www.fogra.org
Vendor:     http://www.fogra.org
License:    zlib
Version:    0.5
%description  target-fogra
Printing characterisation data according to ISO 12647-2.
These are CMYK characterisation data for coated,
webcoated, uncoated, uncoatedyellowish and SC paper.

%package      target-npes
Summary:    NPES Printing Characterisation Data
Group:      Applications/Graphics
URL:        http://www.npes.org
Vendor:     http://www.npes.org
License:    zlib
Version:    0.5
%description  target-npes
Printing characterisation data. These are CMYK
characterisation data for GRACoL, SWOP and SNAP.


